  <h1>Privacy Policy（隐私政策）</h1>
  <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> December 25, 2025</p>

  <h2>English</h2>
  <p>This privacy policy applies to the app "<strong>ICV-Lab</strong>" (hereinafter referred to as "the App") developed by Jankin Sun.</p>

  <p>The App does **not collect, store, share, or transmit any personal data** from its users.</p>

  <p>No third-party analytics tools (e.g., Google Analytics, Firebase), advertising SDKs (e.g., AdMob), or tracking technologies are integrated into the App.</p>

  <p>All functionality is processed locally on your device. No information leaves your iPhone or iPad.</p>

  <p>By using this App, you acknowledge and agree that no data is being collected.</p>

  <h2>中文</h2>
  <p>本隐私政策适用于由 [你的姓名或公司名称] 开发的应用程序“<strong>ICV-Lab</strong>”（以下简称“本应用”）。</p>

  <p>本应用 **不会收集、存储、共享或传输任何用户的个人数据**。</p>

  <p>本应用未集成任何第三方分析工具（如 Google Analytics、Firebase）、广告 SDK（如 AdMob）或其他追踪技术。</p>

  <p>所有功能均在您的设备本地运行，**没有任何信息会离开您的 iPhone 或 iPad**。</p>

  <p>使用本应用即表示您知悉并同意：我们不会收集任何数据。</p>

